;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-1 fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-one\" style=\"--awb-font-size:26px;\"><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h1 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Be Vietnam Pro&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-size:1em;line-height:1.7;\">V\u1eca TR\u00cd VINHOMES H\u1ea2I V\u00c2N BAY<\/h1><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-right\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-1\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed <a href=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/\"><strong>Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong><\/a> t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i L\u00e0ng V\u00e2n, ph\u01b0\u1eddng H\u00f2a Hi\u1ec7p B\u1eafc, qu\u1eadn Li\u00ean Chi\u1ec3u, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng &#8211; m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ecba l\u00fd \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3, n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00e8o H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u00f4m tr\u1ecdn v\u1ecbnh Nam Ch\u01a1n th\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &#8220;vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc qu\u00fd \u1ea9n m\u00ecnh&#8221; c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n Trung, n\u01a1i thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean ban t\u1eb7ng th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea5t &#8220;t\u1ef1a s\u01a1n, h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u1ee7y&#8221; c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3nh quan bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed3i nguy\u00ean s\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ef1a tranh v\u1ebd. V\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 512 hecta, <strong>Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong> n\u00e0y s\u1edf h\u1eefu v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00f4n tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p Vi\u1ec7t Nam, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u1ea3 nhu c\u1ea7u an c\u01b0 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 sinh l\u1eddi b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-2 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay n\u1eb1m ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00e8o H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n, \u00f4m tr\u1ecdn v\u1ecbnh Nam Ch\u01a1n th\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng, h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 th\u1ebf \u201ct\u1ef1a s\u01a1n h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u1ee7y\u201d hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb s\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u.\" title=\"vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-vinh-nam-chon-deo-hai-van.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-vinh-nam-chon-deo-hai-van.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-vinh-nam-chon-deo-hai-van.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5447\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201080%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-vinh-nam-chon-deo-hai-van.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-vinh-nam-chon-deo-hai-van.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-vinh-nam-chon-deo-hai-van.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-vinh-nam-chon-deo-hai-van.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-vinh-nam-chon-deo-hai-van.jpg-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-vinh-nam-chon-deo-hai-van.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-2\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n, bao quanh b\u1edfi n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n h\u00f9ng v\u0129, m\u1edf ra kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean s\u01a1.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-3\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean \u01b0u \u00e1i ban t\u1eb7ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba th\u1ebf v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. T\u1ecda l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i c\u1eeda ng\u00f5 T\u00e2y B\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u1eb1m ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00e8o H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n &#8211; m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng cung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ven bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1eb9p b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 ranh gi\u1edbi t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean gi\u1eefa \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00e0 Th\u1eeba Thi\u00ean Hu\u1ebf, n\u01a1i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 kh\u00ed thi\u00eang tr\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 mang trong m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ngh\u00ecn n\u0103m.<\/p>\n<p>Ph\u00eda B\u1eafc d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u00e0 d\u00e3y n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n h\u00f9ng v\u0129 thu\u1ed9c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Tr\u01b0\u1eddng S\u01a1n, t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh <strong>&#8220;t\u1ea5m b\u00ecnh phong t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean&#8221;<\/strong> che ch\u1edf v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. Ph\u00eda Nam v\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u1ecbnh Nam Ch\u01a1n r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi l\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbc trong xanh nh\u01b0 ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch, m\u1edf ra t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn kho\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea1t ra bi\u1ec3n \u0110\u00f4ng. Ph\u00eda T\u00e2y gi\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c khu d\u00e2n c\u01b0 v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a qu\u1eadn Li\u00ean Chi\u1ec3u, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean s\u01a1 v\u00e0 v\u0103n minh hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ecba h\u00ecnh b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o v\u1edbi ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3, gi\u00fap d\u1ef1 \u00e1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1edd bi\u1ec3n tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3nh quan \u0111a d\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb b\u00e3i c\u00e1t tr\u1eafng m\u1ecbn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u0169i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh. S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa n\u00fai, bi\u1ec3n, r\u1eebng v\u00e0 h\u1ed3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u1ee9 tr\u1ee5 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, an c\u01b0 v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kinh doanh.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-3 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"806\" alt=\"Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n, bao quanh b\u1edfi n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n h\u00f9ng v\u0129, m\u1edf ra kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean s\u01a1.\" title=\"vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5446\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27806%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201280%20806%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27806%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-200x126.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-400x252.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-600x378.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-800x504.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg-1200x756.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-ba-mat-giap-bien-nui-hai-van.jpg.jpg 1280w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-4\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n, bao quanh b\u1edfi n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n h\u00f9ng v\u0129, m\u1edf ra kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean s\u01a1.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-5\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i giao th\u00f4ng \u0111a chi\u1ec1u, linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n. D\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean tr\u1ee5c giao th\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng huy\u1ebft m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n<p><strong>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i trong v\u00f2ng 10 ph\u00fat:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u1ea3ng bi\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Li\u00ean Chi\u1ec3u (c\u00e1ch 2km): M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3ng container l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t mi\u1ec1n Trung, \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c<\/li>\n<li>Ga h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a Kim Li\u00ean (c\u00e1ch 2-3km): Trung t\u00e2m logistics quan tr\u1ecdng, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eaft B\u1eafc Nam<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i trong v\u00f2ng 15 ph\u00fat:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>H\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ed9 H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n 1 &amp; 2 (c\u00e1ch 6-8km): C\u1eeda ng\u00f5 quan tr\u1ecdng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh ph\u00eda B\u1eafc, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Th\u1eeba Thi\u00ean Hu\u1ebf<\/li>\n<li>Trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh qu\u1eadn Li\u00ean Chi\u1ec3u: T\u1eadp trung c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh, ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u00f4ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i trong v\u00f2ng 20 ph\u00fat:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Trung t\u00e2m th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng (c\u00e1ch 12km): Tr\u00e1i tim kinh t\u1ebf, v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1<\/li>\n<li>S\u00e2n bay qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: C\u1eeda ng\u00f5 h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t mi\u1ec1n Trung<\/li>\n<li>Ga \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: Tr\u1ea1m d\u1eebng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eaft B\u1eafc Nam<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i trong v\u00f2ng 35 ph\u00fat:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 H\u1ed9i An: Di s\u1ea3n v\u0103n h\u00f3a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng<\/li>\n<li>C\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch sinh th\u00e1i: Su\u1ed1i L\u01b0\u01a1ng, R\u1ea1n Nam \u00d4, b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n L\u0103ng C\u00f4<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng giao th\u00f4ng n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed <strong>Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong>, gi\u00fap c\u01b0 d\u00e2n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, mua s\u1eafm, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 du l\u1ecbch. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n trong khu v\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-4 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"804\" alt=\"V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecba th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c b\u1ea3n hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3, Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc qu\u00fd gi\u1eefa l\u00f2ng \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb phong th\u1ee7y, v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd cho nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.\" title=\"vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5445\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27804%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201280%20804%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271280%27%20height%3D%27804%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-200x126.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-400x251.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-600x377.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-800x503.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg-1200x754.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vi-tri-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-doc-ban-phong-thuy-dau-tu.jpg.jpg 1280w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-6\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n, bao quanh b\u1edfi n\u00fai H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n h\u00f9ng v\u0129, m\u1edf ra kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean s\u01a1.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-7\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p><iframe title=\"D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Sa, X\u00e3 \u0110\u00f4ng H\u1ed9i, Huy\u1ec7n H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay, TP H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.\" src=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/d\/embed?mid=1870zU-fUOh6UfFp5xhFzqhaiVvQzvsI&amp;ehbc=2E312F&amp;noprof=1\" width=\"100%\" height=\"480\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-8\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>T\u1eeb g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edf h\u1eefu v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ecba l\u00fd \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba v\u1edbi ba m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1p bi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao b\u1ecdc b\u1edfi d\u00e3y n\u00fai h\u00f9ng v\u0129. S\u1ef1 khan hi\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u01b0 v\u1eady khi\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n<p>S\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh du l\u1ecbch mi\u1ec1n Trung v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u01b0 H\u1ed9i An, Hu\u1ebf, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng t\u1ea1o ra nhu c\u1ea7u l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cao c\u1ea5p. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay n\u1eb1m ngay trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a chu\u1ed7i \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch n\u00e0y, t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kinh doanh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng sinh l\u1eddi cao.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kinh t\u1ebf bi\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m kinh t\u1ebf, t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n Trung c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c. Nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn xa s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 sinh l\u1eddi trong d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-9\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc qu\u00fd hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecba th\u1ebf phong th\u1ee7y \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ee3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i giao th\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n, ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n to l\u1edbn v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n Trung.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i an c\u01b0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay mang \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng trong l\u00e0nh, th\u01b0 th\u00e1i gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nguy\u00ean s\u01a1 m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec7n nghi hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb gia t\u0103ng b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng trong d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o gi\u1eefa v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ecba l\u00fd \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba, quy ho\u1ea1ch th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a Vingroup khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u00f4ng minh cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t mi\u1ec1n Trung Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-3 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-background-blend-mode:color;--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-background-color:#f5f1e6;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-align-content-flex-start fusion-flex-justify-content-center fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"width:104% !important;max-width:104% !important;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-2 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-2 fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"--awb-text-color:#000000;--awb-margin-top:20px;--awb-font-size:24px;\"><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h2 clas